Additionally, the paper deals with natural language processing tasks, such as text recognition, which could place it in the cs.CL (Computation and Language) sub-category. The paper also discusses the vulnerability of deep learning models to adversarial attacks, which could place it in the cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) sub-category. Finally, the paper proposes a new method for adversarial attacks, which could place it in the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category.
